701164f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 171st Street (East)
701164f-a.text:
1466 to 1454 Grand Concourse, east side, south from East 172nd to East 171st Streets.
September 1921.

701163f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 171st Street (East)
701163f-a.text:
1460 and 1454 Grand Concourse, adjoining and at the N.E. corner of East 171st Street. No. 1460 is shown in part only.on the left.
May 1927.
